hero.headline: Building Intelligent Systems
hero.description: I specialize in creating production-ready AI applications, transforming complex data into actionable insights and intelligent user experiences.

experiences.description: Architected and deployed enterprise-grade AI solutions, including ArabyGPT and content automation engines. Specialized in fine-tuning LLMs, developing scalable RAG pipelines with LangChain, and integrating real-time AI tools for diverse sectors.

Provided expert support for specialized hardware including ID card printers and RFID systems. Gained hands-on experience in hardware diagnostics, firmware integration, and embedded systems troubleshooting.

projects.name: RugAI: Knot Density Estimator
projects.description: AI-powered tool for estimating knots per square centimeter in rug photos using computer vision. Built for rug merchants to automate quality grading.

projects.name: AI Research Paper Generator
projects.description: Web-based Streamlit app that generates academic-style AI research papers using GPT. Useful for mock papers, educational outlines, or brainstorming scientific topics.
